      "date": "2014-04-05 12:14:33.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified-1\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/5af4af54-bcba-11e3-b54d-52540035b04c).  Ran 13 tests.  1 tests failed: replay-single.",
