      "date": "2014-04-10 14:28:31.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHi Lai, it;s fine. Now the lock cache holds a refcount so in this case, if the refcount drops to zero, there is really no user for this lock. Pretty clear.",
